'''Kang and Lubrichs''' were a [[Music/Legends|musical]] [[Band/Legends|duo]] during the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]], who were executed and their music banned as part of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire's]] sweep to eradicate [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] of "questionable" [[Artist/Legends|artists]]. Their music chips were coveted by [[Kardue'sai'Malloc/Legends|Kardue'sai'Malloc]] so highly, that his last request was to make sure that the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] forward them to a well-known collector.

